      • get

        public static PermissionStatus get(TachyonConf conf,
                                   boolean remote)
                            throws IOException
        Creates the PermissionStatus for a file or a directory.
        Parameters:
        conf - the runtime configuration of Tachyon
        remote - true if the request is for creating permission from client side, the username binding into inode will be gotten from AuthorizedClientUser .get().getName(). If the remote is false, the username binding into inode will be gotten from LoginUser.
        Returns:
        the PermissionStatus for a file or a directory
        Throws:
        IOException - when getting login user fails
